Day 13 – ASP.NET Core Model Binding & Validation 

Overview

This project demonstrates Model Binding and Validation in ASP.NET Core MVC using an Employee Form.
It shows how form data from the browser is automatically mapped to a C# model object and validated using Data Annotations before processing.

The project also logs the request pipeline flow using custom middleware.

